Class BillManagerSessionTest

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    junit.framework.Test

    public class BillManagerSessionTest
extends BasicEJBTestCaseAdapter
    Example test for BillManagerSessionBean and BillEntityBean. This example demonstrates how to test session and CMP entity beans. It shows how to use EJBTestModule.createEntityBean(java.lang.String, java.lang.Object) and EJBTestModule.findByPrimaryKey(java.lang.String, java.lang.Object). You don't have to intercept these methods, just the findUnpaid method.
